<h2>textrecipes: Extra 'Recipes' for Text Processing</h2>
<p>Converting text to numerical features requires
    specifically created procedures, which are implemented as steps
    according to the 'recipes' package. These steps allows for
    tokenization, filtering, counting (tf and tfidf) and feature hashing.</p>
